### ==========================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ==========================================

### Đăng ký tài khoản mới
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin Test",
  "email": "admin2@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Đăng nhập (Lấy Token)
# Copy chuỗi token trả về sau khi login thành công và thay vào biến @token ở dòng 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ==========================================
### CUSTOMER (Khách hàng)
### ==========================================

### Xem danh sách Tours (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tours

### Tạo Booking mới (Cần Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "tourId": "60d21b4667d0d8992e610c85",
  "numberOfPeople": 2,
  "totalPrice": 1500000
}

### Hủy Booking (Cần Token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/bookings/60d21b4667d0d8992e610c85/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==========================================
### STAFF / OPERATOR / GUIDE / SALE (Nhân viên)
### ==========================================

### Thêm Tour mới (OPERATOR, ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tours
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Tour Đà Nẵng - Hội An",
  "description": "Tour du lịch 3 ngày 2 đêm",
  "price": 2500000,
  "duration": 3
}

### Sửa thông tin Tour (OPERATOR, ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tours/60d21b4667d0d8992e610c85
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "price": 2600000
}

### Xóa Tour (OPERATOR, ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tours/60d21b4667d0d8992e610c85
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lấy danh sách Khách hàng (OPERATOR, ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lấy lịch trình Tour (GUIDE, ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tạo báo giá (SALE, ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "customerId": "60d21b4667d0d8992e610c85",
  "tourId": "60d21b4667d0d8992e610c85",
  "quotedPrice": 2400000
}


### ==========================================
### ACCOUNTANT (Kế toán)
### ==========================================

### Tạo hóa đơn (ACCOUNTANT, ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bookingId": "60d21b4667d0d8992e610c85",
  "amount": 1500000,
  "status": "PAID"
}

### Xem Báo cáo tài chính (ACCOUNTANT, ADMIN, MANAGER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/financial
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==========================================
### MANAGER / ADMIN (Quản lý)
### ==========================================

### Lấy danh sách Users (MANAGER, ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tạo User mới (MANAGER, ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Tran Van B",
  "email": "manager@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "MANAGER"
}

### Cập nhật User (MANAGER, ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/60d21b4667d0d8992e610c85
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Xóa User (MANAGER, ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/60d21b4667d0d8992e610c85
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Xem báo cáo tổng quan (MANAGER, ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/general
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sao lưu hệ thống (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/backup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
